10#include <stdio.h>
11#include "internal/cryptlib.h"
12#include <openssl/x509.h>
13#include <openssl/asn1t.h>
14
15ASN1_SEQUENCE(NETSCAPE_SPKAC) = {
16 ASN1_SIMPLE(NETSCAPE_SPKAC, pubkey, X509_PUBKEY),
17 ASN1_SIMPLE(NETSCAPE_SPKAC, challenge, ASN1_IA5STRING)
18} ASN1_SEQUENCE_END(NETSCAPE_SPKAC)
19
20IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS(NETSCAPE_SPKAC)
21
22ASN1_SEQUENCE(NETSCAPE_SPKI) = {
23 ASN1_SIMPLE(NETSCAPE_SPKI, spkac, NETSCAPE_SPKAC),
24 ASN1_EMBED(NETSCAPE_SPKI, sig_algor, X509_ALGOR),
25 ASN1_SIMPLE(NETSCAPE_SPKI, signature, ASN1_BIT_STRING)
26} ASN1_SEQUENCE_END(NETSCAPE_SPKI)
27
28IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS(NETSCAPE_SPKI)
